OL,3,CInquest to open into death of Soham
OL,4,Ckiller Ian Huntley
OL,6,FAn inquest is due to open into the
OL,7,Fdeath of Soham killer Ian Huntley, who
OL,8,Fdied days after a prison attack.
OL,10,FThe 52-year-old died in the Royal
OL,11,FVictoria Infirmary in Newcastle on 7
OL,12,FMarch after he was allegedly attacked
OL,13,Fwith a metal bar in a workshop at HMP
OL,14,FFrankland in Durham on 26 February.
OL,16,FThe County Durham and Darlington
OL,17,FCoroner has scheduled an inquest
OL,18,Fopening hearing to be held in Crook,
OL,19,FCounty Durham, on Tuesday (14 April).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
