PN,42702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1776276666
OL,3,CInquest to open into death of Soham
OL,4,Ckiller Ian Huntley
OL,6,FListed under the name Ian Kevin
OL,7,FHuntley, the inquest opening will be
OL,8,Fheard by senior coroner Jeremy
OL,9,FChipperfield.
OL,11,FHuntley was serving a life sentence
OL,12,Ffor the 2002 murders of 10-year-olds
OL,13,FHolly Wells and Jessica Chapman.
OL,15,FThe ex-school caretaker killed the
OL,16,Fbest friends after they left a family
OL,17,Fbarbecue to buy sweets in Soham,
OL,18,FCambridgeshire, on 4 August 2002. He
OL,19,Fdumped their bodies in a ditch 10
OL,20,Fmiles away.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1776276666
OL,3,CInquest to open into death of Soham
OL,4,Ckiller Ian Huntley
OL,6,FThey were not found for 13 days,
OL,7,Fdespite a search involving hundreds of
OL,8,Fpolice.
OL,10,FAt the time, Huntley lived with Maxine
OL,11,FCarr, who was a teaching assistant at
OL,12,FHolly and Jessica's primary school.
OL,14,FHe denied murdering the girls but was
OL,15,Fconvicted after a trial at the Old
OL,16,FBailey in 2003.
OL,18,FHe was jailed for life with a
OL,19,Frecommended minimum term of 40 years.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
