PN,42704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1776276666
OL,3,CInquest to open into death of Soham
OL,4,Ckiller Ian Huntley
OL,6,FCarr gave Huntley a false alibi and
OL,7,Fwas jailed for 21 months for
OL,8,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,10,FShe is now living under a new identity.
OL,12,FAnthony Russell, 43, has been charged
OL,13,Fwith murdering Huntley at the maximum
OL,14,Fsecurity jail.
OL,16,FHe will attend Newcastle Crown Court
OL,17,Fon 24 April for a pre-trial
OL,18,Fpreparation hearing.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
